 &lt;p&gt;⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://leetcode.com/problems/sliding-window-maximum/&#34;&gt;&lt;ins class=&#34;dot&#34;&gt;題目敘述&lt;/ins&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You are given an array of integers  &lt;code&gt;nums&lt;/code&gt; , there is a &lt;span class=&#34;orange&#34;&gt;sliding&lt;/span&gt; window of size  &lt;code&gt;k&lt;/code&gt;  which is moving from the very left of the array to the very right. You can only see the  &lt;code&gt;k&lt;/code&gt;  numbers in the window. Each time the sliding window moves right by one position.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Return &lt;em&gt;the max sliding window&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;example-1&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#example-1&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Example 1&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Input&lt;/strong&gt;: nums = [1,3,-1,-3,5,3,6,7], k = 3&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Output&lt;/strong&gt;: [3,3,5,5,6,7]&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Explanation&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;Window position                Max
---------------               -----
[1  3  -1] -3  5  3  6  7       3
 1 [3  -1  -3] 5  3  6  7       3
 1  3 [-1  -3  5] 3  6  7       5
 1  3  -1 [-3  5  3] 6  7       5
 1  3  -1  -3 [5  3  6] 7       6
 1  3  -1  -3  5 [3  6  7]      7
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;example-2&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#example-2&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Example 2&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Input&lt;/strong&gt;: nums = [1], k = 1&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Output&lt;/strong&gt;: [1]&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;解題思路&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#解題思路&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 解題思路&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use &lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cucHJvZ3JhbWl6LmNvbS9qYXZhLXByb2dyYW1taW5nL2RlcXVl&#34;&gt;Deque&lt;/span&gt; name  &lt;code&gt;dq&lt;/code&gt; .&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Map  &lt;code&gt;k&lt;/code&gt;  integer in the  &lt;code&gt;nums&lt;/code&gt; , and keep the high number in the  &lt;code&gt;dq&lt;/code&gt;  first value.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adding  &lt;code&gt;dp&lt;/code&gt;  first value in  &lt;code&gt;List&lt;/code&gt;  name  &lt;code&gt;res&lt;/code&gt;  which will become the answer.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Making  &lt;code&gt;List&amp;lt;Integer&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;  into  &lt;code&gt;int[]&lt;/code&gt;  and return.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
