&lt;h2 id=&#34;primitive-data-type&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#primitive-data-type&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Primitive Data Type&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;These data types are built-in or predefined data types and can be used directly by the user to declare variables.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
&lt;thead&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th&gt;Data Type&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th&gt;byte&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th&gt;Remark&lt;/th&gt;
